{"tid":1479432,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"816集會起作用，美議員強硬聲明警告中國唔好亂來","createTime":"2019-08-17T01:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T05:06:45.000Z","uid":305299,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"327d159dd6d90df4384d577e7a59d07d5a8695de","tid":1479432,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"喺816集會之後，美國共和黨參議員魯比奧 (Marco Rubio) 發出強硬聲明，警告中國如果夠膽出動解放軍，中國將無法繼續享受香港帶來嘅好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且美國將會迅速採取一系行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />包括取消香港喺美國法律下嘅特殊地位，動用全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法 (Global Magnitsky Act) 制裁中國官員。佢呼籲參議院盡快通過《香港人權及民主法案》。最後仲警告，北京必須喺實踐充分尊重香港自治嘅承諾，或者承受侵略香港後所要面對迅速同嚴重嘅後果，兩者之間作出選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，魯比奧係2014年傘開始，每一屈美國國會都會提交《香港人權及民主法案》，佢係好關心香港，希望美國國會9月復會之後會盡快通過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聲明原文傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/2019/8/rubio-statement-on-china-s-growing-threats-against-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR2tNB85X3i9UagHkh1VnopITICGaczFgSmkMSOsJatR6E-xi6Vhne4X_do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubio.senate.gov%2Fpublic%2Findex.cfm%2F2019%2F8%2Frubio-statement-on-china-s-growing-threats-against-hong-kong%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2tNB85X3i9UagHkh1VnopITICGaczFgSmkMSOsJatR6E-xi6Vhne4X_do&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75fY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=8a14a728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/2019/8/rubio-statement-on-china-s-growing-threats-against-hong-kong?fbclid=IwAR2tNB85X3i9UagHkh1VnopITICGaczFgSmkMSOsJatR6E-xi6Vhne4X_do</a>"},{"pid":"e3a4d7dd7f49f1459b037524195f36d3f2da5019","tid":1479432,"uid":49456,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:59:16.000Z","msg":"Rubio從一而終，好耐之前已經支持我地"},{"pid":"33640f6c4c816139d5a0542608203c98842d1464","tid":1479432,"uid":101113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyT